Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:14.15,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I love you forever with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.74,0:01:32.64,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}每日从早到晚 你都在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:37.20,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这样的生活不断重复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:40.29,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一觉醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:42.80,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你已泡好热咖啡等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:47.38,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}紧紧抱住你的左臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:52.47,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}以前曾屈指等待你的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:57.56,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如今见到你的时间是越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:02:01.87,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,150)\be1}这样的幸福谁曾料到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:07.48,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,200)\be1}你和我 都堕入了爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:12.40,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:15.78,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}初次体会到的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:19.93,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Oh 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.66,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}永远永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:27.52,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此情不变
