Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟蚱蜢面具一起拍照 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为…跟学长在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次约会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟学长一起太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在少女的努力下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的旋转木马高速转起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过少年却似乎有些晕头转向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得认真主动跟她说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前平安夜的惨痛失恋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得少年畏惧恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年啊 哪怕一点点也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拿出勇气和自信
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 果然好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你想来的店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年觉得 自己与此地很不搭调
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里店员穿的制服也很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想过来看这里的制服么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那个…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女含糊其辞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真正的目的并不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这蒂罗尔咖啡厅（Tyrolean Cafe）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是紧靠车站那家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 听说情侣在店里吃了特制香蕉冻糕后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会恩爱到永远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 还有这种传说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女之所以想来这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了吃特制香蕉冻糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后与这少年永远恩爱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女啊 选这位少年真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定好哪样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 怕一个人吃不完…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向最佳情侣比赛冠军进发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的目标是 两人开开心心吃冻糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我开动啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃剩的话 就浪费店员的心血了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我们俩就加油把这个消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那人没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不见少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想胜出最佳情侣比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 时间转瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已是创设祭当天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最佳情侣比赛的日子到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs22}（最佳情侣比赛准备室）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 响比谁都帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很适合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么连七咲都说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很适合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被你们夸 我也高兴不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 为什么响是女孩子呢 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 不过这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么扯淡的情侣真是独此一家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是创造回忆 没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拗不过遥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 难道这小粉红是你搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话 除此之外还能是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开寿司店的搭档自然是鱼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棚町 你竟然笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别瞧不起金枪子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金枪子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 笑得太过了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这金枪子的弹力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天它比鰤江更有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们实在太没礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 纱江好僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我紧张…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很般配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的衣服 是纱江妈妈做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我一说要参赛 妈妈就订做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订做？好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 两位加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也会在观众席为你们打气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的最佳情侣比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参赛人数创历届之最
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战况相当激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丰厚大奖究竟花落谁家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请选手马上登场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 第一组参赛者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年A班 梅原正吉 金枪子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金枪子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 好登对！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢诸位为了我和金枪子前来捧场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:07:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让金枪子幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金枪子 今晚我们俩玩解体秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解体秀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搞通宵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人好像突然间都走光了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是门可罗雀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为体育馆在搞最佳情侣比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都去那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁这会儿好好休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 要沏茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准用之前那俄罗斯转盘沏茶法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只准用普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森岛学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐～ 学姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我来介绍最后一对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:09:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年A班橘纯一 1年A班中多纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当纯情的一对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像是婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟往常的中多不一样 好成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 纱江好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是问答环节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你们喜欢对方的什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘先回答吧 怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那中多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可靠的教官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 教官？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 中多 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 所有情侣都登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在请担任裁判的老师开始评分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠军我拿定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二留给你们好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 你真有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 金枪子跟中多战得难分胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你我之间有着决定性的差异
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 金枪子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年已经懒得继续吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,评分结果出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在公布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本年度的最佳情侣比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裁判一致认定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塚原响 森岛遥 胜出！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在场各位为她们献上热烈掌声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘纯一 中多纱江这一对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是玩噱头才拿到那么多票
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的冠军是那一对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真的好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱得我想带她回家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣登冠军宝座的塚原 森岛学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将获赠山猫屋的晚餐券
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 荣获亚军的橘和中多的奖品是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影院包厢座位票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝这两对过得开心
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能拿到冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是学长的错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…学长比塚原学姐要帅得多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我比不过森岛学姐才失败的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起森岛学姐 还是纱江可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 这电影票…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去看怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 这样好吗 明天是圣诞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然最佳情侣比赛没能胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但两人的奋斗相当精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女不好意思说真话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才谎称是妈妈订做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实那套纯白色的裙子和西服套装
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她亲手缝出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的努力有了回报
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------------以下取自萌月字幕组出品BDRip字幕----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还没到约定的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江 你又提前到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从下次开始只要按时就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也想等等纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 怎么能让学长等我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔一两次不也蛮好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 最近还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:13:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞之约？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 我也想交个男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得纱江变得比搬家之前更可爱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是恋爱的魔力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那多多加油咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶...怎么了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------------以上取自萌月字幕组出品BDRip字幕----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间感觉真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 这椅子坐起来真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江也坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去趟洗手间！  我去买饮料！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真跟她说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\b0\fsp0}（咋了 小哥）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\b0\fsp0}（你爱上镜子了吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\b0\fsp0}（别害怕失恋）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\b0\fsp0}（只要勇敢 肯定行的）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\b0\fsp0}（虽然人无法一直走运）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\b0\fsp0}（加油吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 脱了外套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这里暖气很强 挺热的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 脸很红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有点热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微好点了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是纱江的衣服让我心跳加速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问了美也吧？ 我问了美也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前还担心不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 听说这部电影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍完后才曝出导演和女主角在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导演才能将女主角的美最大限度地表现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以受到一致好评哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在洗手间碰到这导演了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道女主角有没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是情侣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在一起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉导演对女主角的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋溢在整个银幕上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满了爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的思念也没输哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能拍得很美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是导演 纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起 你就是我所拍片中的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 好…好难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 不能躲开镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 来 来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年 不要害怕失败
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有勇气 肯定行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不是伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像现在这样跟学长在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…学长 说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 没办法用语言表达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要认真跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然年长却不可靠 还不会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从跟学长相遇以后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改变了很多 每天都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢纱江的心情 不会输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 我好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年被少女的眼眸直击胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间萌死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的萌死 是指胸口猛地一紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心被夺走 就此升天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}学长——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看起来像情侣么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是货真价实的情侣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪今天那么冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是雪能积起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因失恋创伤而变成胆怯懦夫的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有极度腼腆少女之间的恋爱故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此画上句号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人好不容易迈出了第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们由衷祝福他俩能永远恩爱下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久后 他们俩…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 很好很好 纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下来的姿势…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 又在拍奇怪的电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.95,0:22:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 纱江的企鹅装好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 这个打扮是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我也加入嘛 喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也好可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真开心喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来嘛 快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没辙 给你也拍拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 今后也请将我拍得最可爱哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.07,0:24:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 哥们～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.10,0:24:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了 梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.90,0:24:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然会上预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.50,0:24:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道从下集开始「女主角」是你？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.45,0:24:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.98,0:24:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也是呢 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.10,0:24:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据我的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.04,0:24:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位女主角相当「紧」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.54,0:24:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.26,0:24:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能挺得住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.52,0:25:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 糟透
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.55,0:25:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.23,0:25:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这标题看着很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.92,0:25:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 你做好觉悟吧
